htsschreibung wenig beachteten Typ des Mehrfamilienhauses, der bewusst dem „Mittelmaß“ folgt und doch eine hoch entwickelte Urbanität und Qualität erreicht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecture, DomesticzAustriavExhibitions. 4aArchitektur. 4aBasel. 4aBaumgartner & Hindermann. 4aBaumgartner. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh1 aBrandenberger, Rebekka, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDegen, Bernard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHuber, Dorothee, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStalder, Laurent, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZophoniasson, Ulrike, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aZophoniasson, Ulrike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZünd, Marco, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aZünd, Marco, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2010z9783110233544oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET KUNST UND ARCHITEKTUR 2010z9783110318876oZDB-23-DKA40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303461082740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783034610827423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783034610827/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2010  aZDB-23-DKAb2010  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014